---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section id="testimonials" class="bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100 reveal-section">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8 py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <Icon name="solar:chat-square-like-bold-duotone" size={40} class="text-neutral-300 mb-10" />
      <p class="serif reveal-text" style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif; font-size:clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); line-height:1.2; letter-spacing:-0.02em; color:#171717;">
        &ldquo;Marcus didn&rsquo;t just redesign our brand &mdash; he gave us a language we could finally rally behind. Every touchpoint feels intentional now.&rdquo;
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-neutral-500 mt-8 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl reveal-fade">
        From the initial audit to the final guidelines, the Orbit team immersed themselves in our culture and delivered a brand system that&rsquo;s elevated how we show up across every channel. Truly transformative partnership.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-10 reveal-fade">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=320&q=80"
          alt="Sofia Martinez"
          class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="48"
          height="48"
        />
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Sofia Martinez</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">VP of Brand, TechNova</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
